latestPosts.caption:
🇺🇸✨Save this for your 4th of July morning✨🇺🇸

Start the day feeling good before the burgers & bevvies hit 

Red, White, and Blueberry Gut Health Smoothie 👇
INGREDIENTS: 
❤️Red layer
• 1/2c Suja Gut Health Berry Lemon
• 1/2c frozen raspberries 
• 1/2 c frozen strawberries
🤍 White layer 
• 1/3c coconut milk
• 3/4c ice
• 2 tsp agave 
💙Blue layer
• blueberries

PREPARATION: 
1. Blend your red layer, pour it into a glass
2. Blend your white layer, gently pour on top
3. Add fresh blueberries + a festive straw

#4thofjulymorning #smoothie #july4thfood #summer25 #guthealth #probioticos
